MORIKO Camping Lights Rechargeable Telescopic, Portable Collapsible Magnetic Lantern Camping Essentials, 10,500mAh IP67 Water

Versatile Dual Light Source Design: Our camping light offers a powerful dual light source, functioning as both a flashlight and a floodlight. With four lighting modes including flashlight mode (100m beam range), floodlight mode (wide angle illumination), SOS mode, and strobe mode, this versatile light is perfect for any outdoor or emergency situation

Portable and Easy to Use: Featuring a retractable, foldable, and magnetic tripod design, our camping light is incredibly easy to carry and store, ideal for limited space in camping backpacks. The extendable lamp pole can illuminate hard-to-reach areas like tent tops or narrow corners. The tripod can stand stably on flat ground, grass, or sand, and the built-in magnet allows it to attach securely to cars, boats, or motorcycles

Customizable Brightness and Color Temperature: With three brightness levels (for both floodlight and flashlight) and a freely adjustable color temperature range of 1800K-6500K (floodlight only), users can customize their lighting experience according to their environment. Perfect for reading, working, or outdoor camping, it adapts to multiple scenarios

Durable and Waterproof: The lamp head is made of aluminum alloy, providing wear and scratch resistance, and boasts an IP67 waterproof rating, making it suitable for water-related activities like night fishing. The lamp body is constructed from impact-resistant, high-temperature resistant, and recyclable PC material with an IP54 waterproof rating, ensuring it withstands extreme weather conditions

Extended Battery Life with Dual Functionality: Equipped with a 10,500mAh large capacity battery, our camping light can provide up to 33 hours of continuous illumination. It also doubles as a power bank, capable of charging phones, tablets, and headphones, ensuring you don't have to worry about power issues during your camping or outdoor adventures

At Moriko, we are passionate explorers inspired by the beauty of the great outdoors. Our journey began with a desire to craft reliable, innovative outdoor products that not only elevate your adventures but also reconnect you with nature. From versatile camping lights to efficient outdoor showers and camping fan, our product line is thoughtfully designed to enhance your outdoor experience, making every moment comfortable and memorable.

We believe that great design is at the heart of every adventure. Each Moriko product combines functionality and cutting-edge design, ensuring they meet the demands of both casual campers and seasoned explorers. Durability and practicality are our guiding principles.

With deep respect for nature and a commitment to sustainability, we carefully choose materials that withstand the test of time. Our products reflect a harmony between innovative design and nature-inspired craftsmanship.
